data.description: Exceptional modern living in Martha's Vineyard Gated Community! Nearly new custom-built home has 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, LARGE game room, and den. The primary suite is nestled on the first floor. The interior of the home offers an open floor plan, soaring ceilings, natural lighting, granite counters, and a double oven. The second floor includes three spacious bedrooms, two generous-sized bathrooms, and a large game room. Additional bonuses include ethernet ports in every room, updated bathroom fixtures as well as tile and a tankless water heater. The community is gated and offers many family-friendly outdoor activities to enjoy. Easy access to I-45 and 288. Galveston is also a short drive away for those weekend getaways. Photos DO NOT do it justice. Call today for an appointment!
